jakarta.nosql.mapping.document

Interface DocumentQueryMapper.DocumentMapperQueryBuild

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DocumentQueryMapper.DocumentMapperFrom, DocumentQueryMapper.DocumentMapperLimit, DocumentQueryMapper.DocumentMapperNameOrder, DocumentQueryMapper.DocumentMapperSkip, DocumentQueryMapper.DocumentMapperWhere
    Enclosing interface:
    DocumentQueryMapper

    public static interface DocumentQueryMapper.DocumentMapperQueryBuild
    The last step to the build of DocumentQuery. It either can return a new DocumentQuery instance or execute a query with DocumentTemplate and DocumentTemplateAsync
